rom accredited projects to early access</em> ).<br />\r\n&nbsp;- <strong>Portfolio Creation </strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;( <em>CV/Resume creation, Employment, Qualifications, Publications, Articles</em> )<br />\r\n&nbsp;-&nbsp;<strong>Tutorials</strong></p>\r\n' , 'Accredited' , '99.99' , '100' , '10' , '2018-11-09' , '2019-01-30' ); INSERT INTO salesoptions VALUES('9' , 'Premium Steven' , 'subscription' , '<p>Keep 100% of your earnings*, for small companies and individuals this is a great option.<br />\r\n<strong>Price: </strong>$200 / Year</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u>Access to:</u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;-<strong> Freelance&nbsp;Projects&nbsp; &nbsp;- Unlimited Access</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;( <em>creation and bidding, Early Access</em> )<br />\r\n&nbsp;- <strong>Software Market - Unlimited Access.</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;( <em>Selling completed websites, domain names, code, templates etc</em> )<br />\r\n&nbsp;- <strong>Local Jobs</strong>&nbsp;<strong>- Unlimited Access.</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;( <em>Listing Jobs and Acting as a Recruitment Consultant</em> )<br />\r\n&nbsp;- <strong>Portfolio Creation</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;( <em>CV/Resume creation, Employment, Qualifications, Publications, Articles</em> )<br />\r\n&nbsp;-&nbsp;<strong>Tutorials</strong></p>\r\n' , 'Premium' , '99.99' , '0' , '0' , '2018-11-09' , '2019-01-30' ); INSERT INTO salesoptions VALUES('10' , 'List Software' , 'software' , 'List one Software' , 'Entry' , '4.99' , '5' , '0' , '2019-01-30' , '2019-01-30' ); INSERT INTO salesoptions VALUES('11' , 'List 5 software for the price of 4' , 'software' , 'List 5 software for the price of 4' , 'Entry' , '19.99' , '25' , '20' , '2019-01-30' , '2019-01-30' ); INSERT INTO salesoptions VALUES('12' , 'Unlimited Everything' , 'software' , 'List <strong>Unlimited</strong> Jobs<br />\r\n<strong>Unlimited</strong> Job Applications<br />\r\n<strong>Unlimited</strong> access to sell in the Software Market<br />\r\n<strong>Unlimited</strong> access to list Freelance Projects and also to bid on other Freelance Projects<br />\r\n<strong>$200 / Year Unlimited Access</strong>' , 'Premium' , '99.99' , '0' , '0' , '2019-01-30' , '2019-01-30' );